  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nPPA package requires curl, but does not list it as a dependency\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Set up the PPA nethermind repository.\r\n2. `apt remove curl`\r\n3. `apt install nethermind`\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nNethermind is installed correctly\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior**\r\nNethermind fails to get its binaries off github because curl is required but not listed as a dependency\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - OS: Ubuntu 20.04 LTS\r\n",
